    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a full-round action, you can summon a single ice elemental (Pathfinder&nbsp;RPG Bestiary 2&nbsp;114) to serve you.</p>\n<p>At 7th level, you can summon a Medium ice elemental, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.aqri3zf6mzgd4di6]{Summon Monster IV}.</p>\n<p>At 11th level, you can summon a Huge ice elemental, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.mf6k8tg8xu0wedoz]{Summon Monster VI}.</p>\n<p>At 15th level, you can summon an elder ice elemental, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.j91n23p4tfjixp3s]{Summon Monster VIII}.</p>\n<p>You can use this ability once per day, plus one additional time per day at 15th level.</p>\n<p>You must be at least 7th level before selecting this revelation.</p>",
